{"tid":843152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果元朗稱為市，香港是否一個國家？","createTime":"2018-10-01T02:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T02:54:57.000Z","uid":17177,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f948a552a8da2ea22e3936a8b9ffb0bf0ca6689","tid":843152,"uid":17177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/104421_e3449a2e658ae429d49309465d751e9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F104421_e3449a2e658ae429d49309465d751e9c.png&h=3530e36f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市是一個國家之行政區劃單位，通常運用於城市，有時會另稱「建制市」以便與地理學或文化（約定俗成）上的都市區別。市建制基本反應其城鎮化水平和城市化發展趨勢。一個市通常會劃分為數個行政區，以方便政府之治理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/市\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%B8%82&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrInjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=daa6ff9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/市</a> from 維基<br />\n<br />\n香港幾時建國架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通10月1日係真&middot;香港國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb57c3da76c752ded563cf82f6c7ac8405b0ed9","tid":843152,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"香港省"},{"pid":"cf41e07ae2171c87ccc85f152891b103393d7a43","tid":843152,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"建立<br />\n天水圍國<br />\n元朗國<br />\n上水國<br />\n<br />\n作為香港同支國的緩衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adf6f14dbc4a09be540f14ab322034caee1ab61","tid":843152,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:54:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被